<body><br>
    <h2 id="names">Work Of:- Ansel Adams</h2>
    <main>
        <article>
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1526134679303-e64bf84c176e?q=80&w=1770&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="italian pasta">
            <h2>Rustic Elegance</h2>
            <h3>Project Date: 2016 A.D</h3>
            <p> Exploring the beauty of rustic settings, incorporating elements of elegance and luxury. Capture the harmonious blend of old and new, highlighting the timeless appeal of rustic charm. Consider photographing vintage objects, rustic architecture, natural landscapes, and still life compositions. Use earthy tones, soft natural light, and thoughtful composition to create visually stunning and emotionally resonant images.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1710572093532-06531c3cd2c1?q=80&w=1932&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Nepali MoMo">
            <h2>A Tranquil Oasis</h2>
            <h3>Project Date: 2019 A.D</h3>
            <p>Creating a peaceful and serene visual narrative of tranquil oases. Capture the beauty of natural settings, such as gardens, lakes, or forests, where tranquility and serenity abound. Focus on capturing the calming atmosphere, soft lighting, and peaceful details that evoke a sense of tranquility and relaxation. Consider photographing serene landscapes, tranquil bodies of water, peaceful wildlife, or people enjoying the peaceful ambiance. Use soft, muted colors, gentle compositions, and a focus on detail to create a visually soothing and emotionally uplifting project.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1575977825185-ed5b1a5bd571?q=80&w=1770&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Mountain Image">
            <h2>A Himalayan Tapestry</h2>
            <h3>Project Date: 2024 A.D (Ongoing)</h3>
            <p>Explore the majestic beauty and cultural richness of the Himalayas through a visual tapestry. Capture the grandeur of the mountains, the diversity of the landscapes, and the vibrant culture of the region. Focus on capturing the awe-inspiring beauty of the peaks, the serene beauty of the valleys, and the unique traditions and customs of the people. Consider photographing the majestic mountains, serene valleys, colorful villages, ancient monasteries, and local people in their traditional attire. Use a variety of perspectives, colors, and compositions to create a visually stunning and culturally rich project that celebrates the beauty and diversity of the Himalayas.</p>
        </article>
</main>

<h2 id="names">Work Of:- Frida Kahlo</h2>
<main>
        <article>
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1682687981907-170c006e3744?q=80&w=1771&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Mountain Image">
            <h2>Underwater Paradise</h2>
            <h3>Project Date: 2018 A.D</h3>
            <p>Explore the vibrant and mysterious world beneath the waves. Capture the stunning beauty of marine life, coral reefs, and underwater landscapes. Focus on capturing the diversity of marine creatures, the intricate details of coral reefs, and the play of light in the water. Consider photographing colorful fish, unique marine mammals, vibrant coral reefs, and underwater caves. Use a variety of underwater photography techniques to create a visually stunning and informative project that celebrates the beauty and diversity of the underwater world.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1654607351830-c00fda86b329?q=80&w=1932&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Mountain Image">
            <h2>Serene Sunset Over Phewa Lake</h2>
            <h3>Project Date: 2021 A.D</h3>
            <p>Capture the breathtaking beauty of a serene sunset over Phewa Lake. Focus on capturing the soft, golden light reflecting on the water, the silhouettes of the surrounding mountains, and the peaceful atmosphere. Consider photographing the setting sun, the lake's reflections, the surrounding mountains, and any boats or people on the lake. Use a long exposure to capture the smooth, silky water and the vibrant colors of the sky. Create a visually stunning and emotionally evocative project that celebrates the beauty and tranquility of Phewa Lake at sunset.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1537210249814-b9a10a161ae4?q=80&w=1932&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Mountain Image">
            <h2> Nature's Fury</h2>
            <h3>Project Date: 2023 A.D</h3>
            <p>Capture the raw power and destructive beauty of nature's fury. Focus on documenting the aftermath of natural disasters, such as storms, earthquakes, or wildfires. Consider photographing the destruction caused by the natural disaster, the resilience of nature, and the impact on communities. Use a variety of perspectives and techniques to create a visually powerful and informative project that raises awareness about the destructive force of nature and the importance of disaster preparedness.</p>
        </article>
    </main>

<h2 id="names">Work Of:- Georgia O'Keeffe</h2>
<main>
        <article>
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1661698579912-13e55b29f6e9?q=80&w=1931&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Mountain Image">
            <h2>Stormy Skies Over Kathmandu</h2>
            <h3>Project Date: 2019 A.D</h3>
            <p>Capture the dramatic and awe-inspiring beauty of stormy skies over Kathmandu. Focus on capturing the dark clouds, lightning, rain, and the city skyline. Consider photographing the storm from different angles and perspectives, highlighting the contrast between the city and the natural elements. Use a variety of techniques, such as long exposures and HDR, to create visually striking and emotionally impactful images.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512036594830-51cea3a8df78?q=80&w=1918&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Mountain Image">
            <h2>Serene Valley in Nepal</h2>
            <h3>Project Date: 2020 A.D</h3>
            <p>Explore the peaceful and picturesque beauty of a serene valley in Nepal. Focus on capturing the lush greenery, mountains, rivers, and villages. Consider photographing the valley from different vantage points, highlighting the harmony between nature and human settlements. Use soft, natural light and a focus on detail to create a visually calming and emotionally uplifting project.</p>
        </article>
        <article>
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604521241808-a4263e067d79?q=80&w=1770&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D" alt="Mountain Image">
            <h2>Red Fox on the Prowl</h2>
            <h3>Project Date: 2024 A.D</h3>
            <p>Capture the elusive and fascinating beauty of a red fox in its natural habitat. Focus on capturing the fox's stealth, agility, and intelligence. Consider photographing the fox hunting, playing, or resting in its natural environment. Use a variety of techniques, such as camouflage and patience, to capture the fox in its natural habitat. Create a visually stunning and informative project that celebrates the beauty and mystery of the red fox.</p>
        </article>
    </main>

